defaultThe coaching needs for boys and girls appear to be different. Boys tell us they want an experienced and qualified coach, wh
defaultile girls have told us the qualities they need are an understanding and empathetic coach. To this end we have 
defaultjust completed working with Us Girls (through Streetgames) to deliver sessions to all our County FA staff on the importance of tailoring sessions 
defaultto the needs and motivations of 
defaultyoung female players
