default28.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultCe
defaultntral to meeting the physical literacy challenge is addressing the deficiency in sport and physical education experience amongst teaching staff in the primary sector and the access to high quality PE provision for boys and girls under the age of 11.
