default29.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultGiven
default that the WSFF has identified that 
defaultthe level of coaching 
defaultand lack of support from schools are key factors in the drop out from girls football, increasing the number of teachers with a sporting interest and training and up-skilling those to deliver quality 
defaultPE is essential. The FA welcome’s the Government’s current pilot projects which aim to up-skill PE teachers, but would nevertheless hope for further increases in physical education training during Initial Teacher Training. 
