defaultboth boys and girls receive this investment would be welcome
default. 
defaultIn America investment in school sport must be equitable. While this requirement (known as Ti
defaulttle 9) was largely introduced to curb high spending on American Football teams and is perhaps not directly transferable to the UK, the principle of equitable investment for schools is one worth considering here too. 
